title: Proctor Silex 24-Pound Electric Roaster Oven with Variable Temperature Control, Self-Basting Lid & Removable Pan, 18 Quart, Black (32211)
description: The versatile 18 quart Proctor Silex® Electric Roaster Oven with Self-Basting Lid is perfect for holidays and special occasions. It cooks a 24 lb. turkey but also does more. It bakes, roasts, steams, slow cooks and keeps food warm for serving.
